tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE calibration_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  device_id INT,
  log_date TIMESTAMP,
  calibration_success BOOLEAN,
  report TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE quantum_devices (
    device_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    device_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    calibration_date DATE,
    calibration_type VARCHAR(50),
    calibration_value FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE device_calibrations (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    device_id INT REFERENCES quantum_devices(device_id),
    parameter_id INT REFERENCES calibration_parameters(parameter_id),
    calibration_result FLOAT,
    calibration_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE calibration_history (
   calibration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
   device_id INT,
   calibration_date DATE,
   calibrated_by VARCHAR(50),
   notes TEXT
);
